But after adding a bit of colour to the pictures , the retired medical physicist realised he was creating works of art .

He said : ` Nature is amazing under X-rays - it really shows the complexity of the animals and plants .

` My principal objective is now to use X-rays to show the beautifulness of nature . '

Monkeys , fish , birds and reptiles all feature in Mr va n't Riet 's collection , but they are all dead .

